metadata.title: Supco DE526 Dryer Lint Screen Replaces W10717210, 348851, 689465, 8557857, 8557882, 8559787, 8565972, W10641634
features: DRYER LINT SCREEN - The lint screen captures lint as it exits the dryer vent. Periodic replacement of your lint filter will help extend the lifespan of your appliance.
PRODUCT SPECIFICATIONS - The dryer lint screen has a white plastic frame with fine mesh metal screen. It measures 22.25 x 8.00 inches.
PREMIUM REPLACEMENT - This Supco part is an excellent replacement for Whirlpool brand dryers including Whirlpool, Maytag, KitchenAid, Jenn-Air, Amana, Magic Chef, Admiral, Norge, Roper, and others.
HIGHEST QUALITY PARTS - The Supco DE526 meets or exceeds OEM specifications. Supco parts are built to last and popular among repair technicians and DIYers.
description: This dryer lint screen is a direct replacement for Whirlpool brand dryers. This high-quality part, Model No. DE526 is designed to meet or exceed OEM specifications. Supco parts are built to last and popular among repair technicians and DIYers.
White plastic frame with fine mesh metal screen
